name: Robotezos #10
description:
Cardanobot x Solarobotic


"Cardanobot" has 6 Chimneys, which allows him to fly at the speed of an F-16 aircraft, with rigid springs. cardanobot can jump at the speed of ultrasonic reflection. whoever is near it will surely be destroyed

"Solarobotic", has hands in the form of a dragon, which is used to ward off attacks from the side. With eyes on the shoulders, Solarobotic can see enemies from all directions. with a thorny badr, whoever will attack it. must have been killed.

keep up with the excitement of the Robotezos story and roadmap, on the official twitter account: https://twitter.com/robotezos and don't forget our NFT collection. who will mint with 1000 supply, and many other surprises.
